			<div class="feature-block__content">
				<h2>Agents in the meeting</h2>
				<p>Building agentic AI today means stitching together meeting join logic, media pipelines, auth, and custom UIs — before your agent does any actual work. Sonesse removes that entire layer. One API deploys your agents into Teams, Google Meet, or Zoom as native participants. Bring your own avatar engine, voice model, or LLM — swap providers anytime without touching your integration. Your engineers focus on agent logic, not infrastructure.</p>
				<p>Whether it's powering live voice, video, or workflow automation, your AI connects directly into the meeting environment — not bolted on afterwards. With Sonesse, your agents interact and engage in real time with low latency — making it effortless to deliver dynamic, responsive AI experiences where they matter most.</p>
			</div>
		</div>

		<!-- Vendor Agnostic -->
		<div class="feature-block feature-block--reverse">
			<div class="feature-block__content">
				<h2>Embedded workflow</h2>
				<p>Every control lives inside the tool your users already have open — Adaptive Cards in Teams, Zoom Apps panels in Zoom, embedded controls in Google Meet. Video and voice quality stay native. Agents write into meeting chat in real time with links, summaries, and follow-up actions. No separate product to learn. Just a participant in the meeting, controlled through surfaces they already use.</p>
				<p>By providing one API across Zoom, Teams, and Google Meet, we remove platform-specific complexity and make it simple to deploy agents that act, speak, and listen in real time. From SaaS products to enterprise workflows and conversational AI vendors, Sonesse ensures your agents run everywhere — naturally, intelligently, and without delay.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="feature-block__image feature-block__image--centered">
				<img src="/assets/2024/12/voice2.svg" alt="" width="391" height="299" />
			</div>
		</div>

		<!-- Build in Minutes -->
		<div class="feature-block">
			<div class="feature-block__image feature-block__image--padded">
				<img src="/assets/2024/12/Group-299.png" alt="" width="518" height="457" />
			</div>
			<div class="feature-block__content">
				<h2>Simple integration</h2>
				<p>An admin clicks a consent link, approves a limited set of API permissions, and assigns users through their existing identity provider — Entra, Google Workspace, or Zoom admin portal. AI agents start joining meetings as native participants, governed by your existing policies and compliance controls. No code, no installs, no infrastructure. Live in hours, not months.</p>
				<p>Our marketplace API makes it simple to schedule, join, stream, transcribe, and interact. From note-taking and transcription to real-time coaching and workflow execution, your team can go from concept to deployment in minutes — not weeks.</p>
				<p>Let Sonesse take on the complexity of scale, latency, and compliance. You focus on building the intelligence — we handle the engineering.</p>
